  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Any creature that grasps, is grabbed, or comes into prolonged direct contact your’s mold-filled fur must succeed in a DC 12 Constitution saving throw or gain the poisoned condition for 1 minute. A poisoned creature no longer in direct contact with you can re-roll the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the poisoning condition if successful.</p>",
